Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.65,0:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch us if you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten so mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom, I've gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fine on my own now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I could help Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go on a trip together?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.13,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember Yasui from the Kariba Hot Springs?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From back when I had you get me this tea cup.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, on the summer trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chatted with him a few times since then,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and he asked me to come help him with a pottery class he's holding.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming, Touko?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.40,0:03:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised to go shopping with some friends that day,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so you two go have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The class is just going to cover the basics with kids from around the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can turn him down if you're busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.78,0:03:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have plans with your friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you moaning just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been dreaming.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lick it, it'll be fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.03,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning on having the middle-rank demons take care of you while I went to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A hot spring?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.15,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning on going to a hot spring without me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You shouldn't move around too much yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kariba springs won't heal a spirit's wounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoe! Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were hurt, so I came to visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cold greeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You were hit with a cursed arrow, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll take some time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it would heal quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.76,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.25,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,From our perspective, it's just a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.02,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it takes time for a spirit as powerful as Madara to regain his energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.53,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he can't go on the trip after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize to Shigeru, and then...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.83,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a medicinal herb called hazegrass that grows around there.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazegrass?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a medicinal herb for spirits. Normal people can't see it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.83,0:05:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It grows on trees that are many decades old.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you grind it up and apply it to a demon's wounds, they'll heal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it, but take me to the hot springs anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.25,0:05:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go on the trip, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Madara, we've come to visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a visit!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.28,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the white pig cat was injured, so I came to see for myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh hello, Mistress Hinoe.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a drink!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's late!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are making too much noise— oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would probably be worse for his wounds to stay here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem tired, Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was up late packing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.86,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place that sells good lunches on the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go there for lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this what it feels like to go on a trip with your dad?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a bit embarrassing, but it feels nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.37,0:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sitting across from him, but I don't really know what to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Young people aren't too interested in pottery, are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm making you come along for an old man's hobby. Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked the tea cup I got last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always liked the feeling of pottery.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels cold, but somehow warm...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,like soil, I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've always wanted to try making it myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.24,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's new for me to have a conversation with him like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what humans wear on their arms!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.58,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've often seen you come here to watch the human trains.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.05,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the rock you're standing on.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say I'm the avatar of this rock.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.92,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be worshiped by the villagers here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Worshiped... are you a god?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The humans decided to worship me on their own. I never asked them to.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here to watch the trains often,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but are they that interesting?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.24,0:08:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just come here because I might see Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When he doesn't show up, I get disappointed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I come anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.75,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume...  is that a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.63,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's my friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're wearing a watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A watch?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.61,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A device that humans made to measure time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't moving a moment ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think wearing that will make you more human?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,More human?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.34,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to be a great fox like my mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's something you don't need.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It measures human time.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Human time?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natsume came to see me again!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not as weak as I used to be, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind feels good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been a whole year...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if he's doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The person Natsume lives with.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to get that pair of teacups last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lead you to the studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, look over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's carrying a human trinket!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The beast thinks he's human?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.01,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This brat can't even transform!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, partner!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be as easy as last time!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry! You can keep it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Freakin' beasts!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.02,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the place my mom told me never to go to.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.28,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we'll fire the pieces we'll make in tomorrow's pottery class.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be done the next day, and then you can take them home.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hot spring out back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get close to Natsume like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's switch places.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.{added missing line}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've come to live with us, I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone still calls me a wimp.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell, since we live together.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So good...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.32,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Natsume come to such a horrible place?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.13,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he come to see me?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.42,0:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only alive when I'm moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't get any air into the clay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.05,0:13:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift me up, wimp!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a wimp!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.23,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't I get any bigger?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start the firing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me with the kiln, Takashi?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.25,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast child, you must not meet with the human anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.41,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, one of you will be sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.41,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well. Everything in this world lives in its own time.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are not always the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans have their time, and spirits have theirs.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.71,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And beasts have their own as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.76,0:14:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume's time and your time are different.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.27,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must find a partner and have children,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.32,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and teach them as wisely as your mother taught you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what it means to live in a beast's time.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.88,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way, Natsume lives in his own time.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.83,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is very different from yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.63,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have your own time, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived the time of a rock.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.83,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was here far before the humans or spirits were born,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.26,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll sit here until time itself ends.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll always be here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.47,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave this place, I will disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lonely here all alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From my perspective, it's not that long a time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it's short either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.28,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We seal the clay in here for the rest of its time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it takes the form we gave it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.18,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's all take a break until the pieces are done baking and are ready to paint.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've promised Yasui I'd go see his other works.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.13,0:16:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not often I get to come here, so I'm going to go wander around for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought it would be easy to find him,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's got his own life, I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.25,0:16:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello. It's Mister Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.61,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.24,0:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know what that little fox is up to?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, him?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.85,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's grown up to be quite the little delinquent.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A delinquent?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He gives us all kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this scar!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You two weren't bullying him again, were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.81,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one other thing I want to know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just wanted to be with Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.21,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't do anything with Mister Natsume here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You met Natsume?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.22,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But he seemed busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was here looking for an herb.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An herb?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.86,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's called hazegrass, and it grows in old trees around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazegrass...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start the painting!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could do something for Natsume...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.87,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bake them for twelve more hours, and they'll be done.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Master, you need to get back to bed!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a storm coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be fine, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natsume...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to give it to Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm almost there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume! Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.89,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You found these for me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.71,0:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, the god saved me...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.86,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I leave this place, I will disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.47,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.09,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me not to meet you anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since one of us would be sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but that's not true, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The watch is broken now...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.42,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember seeing it move!{this line seems awfully short for the amount of time it takes up}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.99,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember meeting the god, what we talked about, and how he saved me...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.89,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure you and I will... will...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.58,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't understand everything \Nthat the fox cub told me,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.47,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I think I understood the meaning of what he learned from the god.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That spirit...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.41,0:21:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must have spent a lot of time \Nwatching the differences
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}between how humans and spirits live their lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You put Nyangoro's face on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.47,0:22:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nicely made.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Nyangoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.53,0:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meetings and partings may just be a moment apart.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.81,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, I want to treasure them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.04,0:24:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten involved with another demon.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do a bunny girl cafe\N for the cultural festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.55,0:24:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have bunny girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.39,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Festivals are all about having fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.60,0:24:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a cat cafe where everybody\N can admire my beauty!
